summary: An ordinance appropriating the sum of $17.10, or so much thereof as may be necessary, from the general fund of the City of Seattle for the purpose of paying the 1907 taxes on a part of lots 2 to 6 and 13 to 16, Burke's 1st Addition, Supplemental Plat of block 3, and on the 1908 taxes on a part of lot 5, block 3, Fern Hill Addition to West Seattle.
